Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 问题无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们的嘉依卡怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 那赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提 若交换人质时我们遭到狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或踩到陷阱 我就会拉动这根绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会引燃炸药 炸飞我们周遭一带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 故弄玄虚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是你们也得同归于尽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是乱破师的战法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保证首先人质成功交换 其它容后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方也是毫不疏忽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红与白

Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇眼鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这数量可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮家伙应该没有结群的习性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被操纵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼自己跳到地上?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我互换了在水中与空气中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若多项知觉失常 任何生物都不能安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招的好处在于 不用担心因魔法本身而误杀对方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正适合用于活捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 真是令我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到来了两个嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到光线就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要回头 快点跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法遮掩视线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 不还是虚张声势嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这次有人碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换暂时中止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此地 不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去追那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候 魔法真是方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能杀出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 返还
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下挨过此劫为先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 你们怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很累的样子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你换了发型?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…这家伙看起像平常的嘉依卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗 那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 虽然也是嘉依卡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 以后再和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 问题是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兄长 即使挪开了瓦砾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们中也没有能驾驶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而再磨蹭下去就要被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能丢在这里了呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 要开动这机车?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮你开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能用魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿意之后和我打一场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 赶紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本无从追迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特乌斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么多弃兽竟能全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边也是 所有线索都被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来单靠我们两人同时抓捕两组嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究是太托大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两名嘉依卡聚在一起究竟是想做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她们中是否有真身都还是未知之数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许反过来 其实都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是皇帝 那妻妾如云一点都不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他为了万无一失地培养出继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给生下来的所有女儿都取了嘉依卡这个名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说所有的嘉依卡都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底我们对嘉依卡一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那更应该全都抓获进行寻问了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们只能寄希望于前往佩利梅拉尔的本队了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 绕路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六国会议期间 此路禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于此前大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫降于加瓦尔尼公爵领的航天要塞索厄拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据悉公爵动用了大量的化石思念料 擅自将要塞起动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需立即遣使者问明公爵真意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过温和!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟将处于联合国管理下的航天要塞私有化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反意昭然若揭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对待逆贼 唯有以武力肃清!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫急莫急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先还是探探对方的态度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我国农民围绕农地划分问题纷争不断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请借助联军之力 予以镇压…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农民的小冲突算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先处理下在我国横行霸道的强盗团伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我国的贫穷问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请举手后再发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何事? 斯坦梅茨大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我克里曼机关正追踪调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「棺姬嘉依卡」一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种民间传说的报告 听了纯属浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在追踪的嘉依卡 实际入手了数样遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其为真身的可信度…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这种天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不如去调停下方才讲到的农民冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是战后复兴机关的分内之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 此事想来正适合克里曼机关出面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位怎看?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若命令如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么? 去镇压农村?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根据马特乌斯的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡一行人已近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了这一步 怎可轻易…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但六国会议的决定不容违逆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 乱破师?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇主 我的假货?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过 现在谁真谁假还说不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬金额 提出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多 我支付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早复兴 贾兹帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬 如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我为金钱而叛主?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 乱破师为了金钱 可以受雇于任何势力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦选定了雇主就绝不会背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们唯一的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗费一生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有战场战斗才是乱破师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 战场 提供 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能当你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 力量 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗 夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路之所往 战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷茫 摇摆 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该准备做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑 提议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要买件武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这品种齐全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道能遇上你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这附近只有这一个大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡平安无事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有人质在你那儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在犹豫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹豫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹豫追随哪边的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁啊 你以前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现重要之人的目的 就是自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那指的是嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是渴望战斗所以才受雇于嘉依卡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那转到红嘉依卡那边不也一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想 其实投靠红嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁更能尽情战斗吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有收获吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 交换的安排定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天黄昏 佩利梅拉尔中央广场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去告知她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁会选哪边呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间地点谈好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上可以回到那俩乱破师身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 反倒被感谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提议 考虑 换主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我 不满?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不满 复兴帝国和复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在目标明确的你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更能尽情地战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论精神还是肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是个烂好人 全身上下都是可乘之隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还老实又固执
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然都是被需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想效力于更需要我的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又何尝不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫大叔 叫达比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 反应淡薄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成我还得喜极而泣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时最为松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁其实挺担心嘉依卡的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保养武器保养个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的 托鲁总是不坦率嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说来着 怕羞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 大大理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 模仿就不能把口吻也模仿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿卡莉的说话方式太难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致盲者 显现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么? 魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛尔玛那家伙 失败了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘉依卡 你不会被人家迷住了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗俗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉嘉依卡 还得请你马上去开车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果托鲁还是选了白嘉依卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那啥 怕羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕羞你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 嘉依卡·托勒庞特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 记忆 缺落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假货 可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初遇到的嘉依卡是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想侍奉的嘉依卡也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我会毫不犹豫地扫清你前路的一切障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重申一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何 咱们的大小姐对你是青睐有加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你带着遗体加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以避免无用的争斗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上你妹妹 听说还有头装铠龙?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说一起来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若照做 我这边的公主 你们打算如何处置?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 不需两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开膛者 显现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪烁者 显现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Flasher
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障眼法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为钢也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢故不怯 钢故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敌 尽无一切踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为灭此凶器也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成 被逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师那边呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事? 两人没问题?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅有人妨碍收集遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还有人想抢夺我们收集的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来该怎么走…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好想一想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 复数 不需
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早 做了结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕山谷 访问者 无人归来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或某处 遗体存在?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此必须访问 绝对生还
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第七集 「不归谷」

